{
  "category": "TC-FP-CONFORMANCE",
  "describes": "Good/bad fingerprint documents for the §4 schema, checked by spec/validate-fingerprint.mjs (validateVaultData over the Appendix-C wrapper). Each case states the expected verdict; bad cases name substrings that MUST appear in the reported errors. This is the §12 good/bad corpus an external producer self-tests against.",
  "vectors": [
